nimal look. The regular cropped fit offers balanced structure with everyday comfort, making it easy to style across casual and streetwear outfits. Crafted from 100% combed cotton and finished with a bio-wash, the fabric feels soft, breathable, and durable for long-lasting wear. With no prints or graphics, this tee remains a versatile wardrobe essential built for effortless styling.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain fabric quality and structure. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the finish.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM premium cotton fabric for a balanced, structured feel. Regular-fit cropped silhouette designed for modern everyday wear. Classic ringer neckline and sleeve contrast detailing. Minimal blank design for versatile styling. Gender-neutral construction suitable for multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for enhanced softness, breathability, and durability.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47546219036826,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47546219069594,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47546219102362,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47546219135130,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00217-Recoveredcopy_11zon.jpg?v=1772786964"},{"product_id":"regular-ringer-cropped-tee-ii","title":"REGULAR RINGER CROPPED TEE II","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Fabric. Minimal Design. 100% Combed Cotton. Ringer Style Neck \u0026amp; Sleeves. Gender-Neutral. Regular-Fit Cropped Silhouette. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 240 GSM ringer cropped T-shirt from Drip Studios blends classic aesthetics with a modern cropped silhouette. Designed with contrasting ringer detailing on the neckline and sleeve hems, it delivers a subtle vintage-inspired edge while maintaining a clean, minimal look. The regular cropped fit offers balanced structure with everyday comfort, making it easy to style across casual and streetwear outfits. Crafted from 100% combed cotton and finished with a bio-wash, the fabric feels soft, breathable, and durable for long-lasting wear. With no prints or graphics, this tee remains a versatile wardrobe essential built for effortless styling.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain fabric quality and structure. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the finish.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM premium cotton fabric for a balanced, structured feel. Regular-fit cropped silhouette designed for modern everyday wear. Classic ringer neckline and sleeve contrast detailing. Minimal blank design for versatile styling. Gender-neutral construction suitable for multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for enhanced softness, breathability, and durability.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47546240663706,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47546240696474,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47546240729242,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47546240762010,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00363copy_11zon.jpg?v=1772787384"},{"product_id":"raglan-cropped-tee-wine","title":"RAGLAN CROPPED TEE - WINE","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium French Terry Cotton. Cropped Silhouette with Raglan Full Sleeves. Minimal Design. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cropped 240 GSM full-sleeve T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted for a clean, super-decent everyday look. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to maintain the fabric’s integrity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM French terry fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Cropped length with full raglan sleeves for a relaxed, modern fit. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton for all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish ensures durability and a smooth hand feel.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47560478032026,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47560478064794,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47560478097562,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47560478130330,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/SWTS2398.webp?v=1773078848"},{"product_id":"regular-cropped-tee-dor-saint","title":"D'OR SAINT - Ltd. Ed.","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Fabric. Cropped Ringer Design. Embroidered Front Detail. 100% Combed Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Regular-Fit Cropped Silhouette. Limited Edition (100 Pieces). Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis exclusive 240 GSM cropped ringer T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted to deliver a refined balance of vintage inspiration and modern luxury. Designed with signature contrast ringer trims on the neckline and sleeves, it features a clean cropped silhouette with a relaxed waist that offers effortless structure and comfort. The front is elevated with a finely embroidered detail that adds a subtle yet premium statement without overpowering the minimal aesthetic. Made from high-grade combed and bio-washed cotton, the fabric feels exceptionally soft, breathable, and durable for everyday wear. Strictly limited to only 100 pieces, this piece is designed for those who appreciate exclusivity, precision, and timeless streetwear luxury.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"99\" data-start=\"60\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order for these colors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and preserve the embroidery. Avoid harsh detergents or bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the structure. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and embroidery finish.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM premium cotton fabric delivering a structured yet comfortable feel. Cropped ringer silhouette with contrast neckline and sleeve trims for a timeless aesthetic. Finely embroidered front detail adding a subtle luxury statement. Regular-fit cropped design with a relaxed waist for balanced structure and movement. Gender-neutral silhouette suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton ensures all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish for enhanced softness and long-term durability. Exclusively limited to only 100 pieces.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47631552643226,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47631552675994,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47631552708762,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47631552741530,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/Copy_of_DSC00085_copy.jpg_11zon_1.webp?v=1773674828"},{"product_id":"raglan-cropped-tee-royal-blue","title":"RAGLAN CROPPED TEE - ROYAL BLUE","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium French Terry Cotton. Cropped Silhouette with Raglan Full Sleeves. Minimal Design. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cropped 240 GSM full-sleeve T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted for a clean, super-decent everyday look. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to maintain the fabric’s integrity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM French terry fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Cropped length with full raglan sleeves for a relaxed, modern fit. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton for all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish ensures durability and a smooth hand feel.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47687865434266,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47687865467034,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47687865499802,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47687865532570,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shop